item.title: By: Loretta Paraguassu
item.dc:creator: Loretta Paraguassu
item.description: Your stories got to me. I couldn't stop reading. It made me remember long ago journeys by Greyhound between San Francisco and Mexico. The characters, indeed. It's a whole different world. And the bus stations! You did make me remember. Happy trails. You're a great storyteller.
item.content:encoded:
